lead_paragraph: JOSEPH--Maurice J. May 23, 1926 - March 24, 2016. Maurice J. Joseph, 89, of Sarasota, FL and New York City died on March 24, 2016. Loving husband, father and grandfather. WWII Navy veteran. Always in our hearts. Services by Toale Brothers, Sarasota, FL. 1/3
